Interview Text:
Abdisa Duguma Interview (part 4)

One time people called me because their cow had given birth but the calf couldn't walk. The people said if the calf walks we will receive your god. I said, "No problem, but first I must ask you a question: the witchcraft thing they gave you to have around your neck, will you give it to me?" She said "No, I paid 500 birr for it (about $25)." So I asked her which one is greater: 500 birr or your calf? She said she wants her calf, and she took it off. 
So I prayed, "Jesus that I saw in my dreams, where are you? I pray in Jesus' name." When I prayed the mother cow came near, made a sound and the calf got up and went to its mom.
Music Video Instructions: Imagine if God's love for us, and ours for him was like this.
